&lt;a class="reference external image-reference" href="/../arch_2013/files_2013/Photo_Diary/20130524/800/800_01_P1360484_4437729-05.jpg"&gt;&lt;img alt="../../../arch_2013/files_2013/Photo_Diary/20130524/800/800_01_P1360484_4437729-05.jpg" src="/../arch_2013/files_2013/Photo_Diary/20130524/800/800_01_P1360484_4437729-05.jpg"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;p class="caption"&gt;愛吹泡泡的James，與留在地上未破掉的泡泡。&lt;/p&gt;
